  N4 --> N5[UI: UI Screens (report/dashboard) + Notification - Surface actions, outcomes, and audit trail to planners for review]
  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced stockouts and expedited shipments, improved service levels with fewer manual interventions, lower waste from smarter reallocation, and measurable protection of margin via constraint-aware decisions and audit trail of automated actions.]
  N3 -->|Agentic confidence high and action wi...| B1[Autonomously execute reallocation/replan via Remote Functions and log action]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Immediate corrective action reduces risk of stockout without human intervention]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Low model confidence or guardrail thr...| B2[Create CWB Lifecycle case routed to planners with recommended options; wait for human approval]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Prevents risky automated changes; ensures human-in-the-loop for sensitive decisions]
  O2 --> End[End]
